{"type":null,"faqId":49875,"title":"华为智能手表_手表如何进行OTA升级？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body31741019\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329052__p10620322172445\">当有新版本时，手表会收到推送通知卡片提醒，可以根据提示向左滑动卡片进行下载和安装。手表不支持手动检测新版本升级。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329052__p8420641\">请确保手表与手机通过蓝牙正常连接。当手机连接至网络，手表放在充电器上时，手表升级包会自动下载。</p></div><div></div></body>","faqTypeId":722,"faqType":"恢复与升级","useful":3,"unUseful":5,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329052","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615862000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10,Mercury-G101,Mercury-G201","visitedTimes":545,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"OTA，升级，取消升级，手动升级","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}